name: Magnetic Woodlands Wallpaper Blue Green Grey
description:
"This magnetic wallpaper, complete with a cast of moveable characters, will bring fairy tales to life in a child's room. Devise an unfolding fairy tale on your wall with a panel of Sian Zeng's bespoke Narrative Magnetic Wallpaper." The Sunday Times

Wallpaper Width: 52cm
Length per roll: 10m
Repeat size: 53cm half drop
Magnet receptive liner: 61cm width (no pattern repeat) 2x5m roll a total of 10m.
The magnet receptive liner is pasted onto the wall first with pre-mixed wallpaper paste. Once it has dried our woodlands wallpaper is pasted on top to create this magnetic woodlands wall.

If you love the wallpaper pattern of our Magnetic woodlands wallpaper, it is also available to purchase as normal wallpaper for £65/10m roll.

Please note that the colours seen on your monitor may differ slightly from the actual colour of the wallpaper. We therefore advise you to order samples of the wallpaper before making your purchase. Wallpaper samples are free with the purchase of the wallpaper. If you are outside of the UK and would like to make an order please contact me for shipping quotes.

If you would like to purchase a sample please click on the link below. When you next order the wallpaper from us we will refund the sample price.

With our dry wipe speech bubbles you will have lots of fun leaving short messages on your fridge or on your magnetic wallpaper to friends and family. The best thing is that you will be able to write on them over and over again, because they are dry wipe able. 
Why not pair up your speech bubble with one of our characters or buildings to create your own story?
The purchase only contains the dry wipe speech bubble cloud magnet and not the other magnets seen in the examples pictures. 

Dimensions: 7cm x5cm

Please note that the colours seen on your monitor may differ slightly from the actual colour of the magnet.

name: Illustrated Office Bear-Pink
description:
This hand screen printed soft toy bear is ideal as a room decoration or as a kid's toy. It will be a cute present for kidadults and kids alike.

One side of the bear is printed with glasses and tie and on the other side the bear is without his glasses and tie.
Printed with solvent free Eco friendly ink onto 100% Caliko, stuffed with child friendly stuffing.

Dimensions: 14 cm x 34 cm / 5,5" x 13.4"

All bears are carefully packaged and can be gift wrapped on request.

name: Little Red And The Wolf Print
description:
A beautifully quirky, limited edition print, originally illustrated by Sian Zeng.
Inspired by the tale of Little Red Riding Hood, Sian constructed many alternative scenarios to the story. One of which is about a skeleton wolf who wishes to look beautiful by putting on a floral lower garment and Little Red who likes to feed him with snake candies. 

Giclee Print on 310 grams archival paper. Limited edition of 50.
A4 size with 4cm white border. Carefully packaged in a cellophane bag and hard cardboard backing to support the print.
